<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Pricing – <%= appName %></title>
  <style>
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0;}
    :root{--bg:#0f1117;--bg2:#1a1d27;--bg3:#21262d;--border:#2a2d3a;--text:#e6edf3;--muted:#8b949e;--blue:#3b82f6;--blue-light:#60a5fa;}
    body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;}
    a{text-decoration:none;}
    nav{background:rgba(15,17,23,0.95);backdrop-filter:blur(10px);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);position:sticky;top:0;z-index:100;}
    .nav-inner{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 24px;height:64px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;}
    .nav-logo{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:var(--blue-light);}
    .nav-links{display:flex;gap:24px;align-items:center;}
    .nav-links a{color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;}
    .btn-nav{background:var(--blue);color:white !important;padding:8px 20px;border-radius:8px;font-size:14px;}
    .nav-links a.nav-active {
      color: var(--text) !important;
      background: rgba(59,130,246,0.12);
      padding: 5px 11px;
      border-radius: 7px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(59,130,246,0.25);
    }
    .page{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px 24px;}
    .page-hero{text-align:center;margin-bottom:60px;}
    .page-hero h1{font-size:42px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:16px;}
    .page-hero p{font-size:18px;color:var(--muted);max-width:480px;margin:0 auto;}
    .pricing-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(280px,1fr));gap:20px;}
    .plan{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:16px;padding:32px;position:relative;}
    .plan.featured{border-color:var(--blue);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--blue);}
    .plan-badge{position:absolute;top:-12px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(--blue);color:white;padding:3px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:12px;font-weight:600;white-space:nowrap;}
    .plan-name{font-size:18px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;}
    .plan-price{font-size:40px;font-weight:800;margin:16px 0 4px;letter-spacing:-0.02em;}
    .plan-period{color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;margin-bottom:24px;}
    .plan-features{list-style:none;margin-bottom:32px;}
    .plan-features li{padding:6px 0;font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);}
    .plan-features li:last-child{border:none;}
    .plan-features li::before{content:'✓ ';color:#22c55e;font-weight:bold;}
    .plan-cta{display:block;text-align:center;padding:12px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;}
    .plan-cta.primary{background:var(--blue);color:white;}
    .plan-cta.secondary{background:var(--bg3);color:var(--text);border:1px solid var(--border);}
    .faq{margin-top:80px;}
    .faq h2{font-size:28px;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:32px;text-align:center;}
    .faq-item{background:var(--bg2);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;padding:20px 24px;margin-bottom:12px;}
    .faq-item h3{font-size:15px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px;}
    .faq-item p{color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;}
    /* Footer handled by shared public-footer partial */
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<nav>
  <div class="nav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="nav-logo"><%= appName %></a>
    <div class="nav-links">
      <a href="/features">Features</a>
      <a href="/pricing" style="color:var(--text);">Pricing</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
      <a href="/security">Security</a>
      <a href="/login" class="btn-nav">Sign In</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>
<div class="page">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <h1>Simple Pricing</h1>
    <p>One platform, one price. All features included. No per-seat fees.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="pricing-grid">
    <div class="plan">
      <div class="plan-name">Starter</div>
      <div class="plan-price">Contact Us</div>
      <div class="plan-period">per workspace / month</div>
      <ul class="plan-features">
        <li>Up to 10 staff</li>
        <li>Up to 10 vehicles</li>
        <li>Live monitoring</li>
        <li>Compliance sheets</li>
        <li>Basic exports</li>
        <li>Event logs</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/login" class="plan-cta secondary">Get Started</a>
    </div>
    <div class="plan featured">
      <div class="plan-badge">Most Popular</div>
      <div class="plan-name">Professional</div>
      <div class="plan-price">Contact Us</div>
      <div class="plan-period">per workspace / month</div>
      <ul class="plan-features">
        <li>Up to 50 staff</li>
        <li>Up to 50 vehicles</li>
        <li>All Starter features</li>
        <li>Custom branding</li>
        <li>Exception reports</li>
        <li>Notification bell</li>
        <li>Monitor board</li>
        <li>Backup &amp; restore</li>
        <li>Custom temp ranges</li>
        <li>Scheduled email exports</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/login" class="plan-cta primary">Get Started</a>
    </div>
    <div class="plan">
      <div class="plan-name">Enterprise</div>
      <div class="plan-price">Contact Us</div>
      <div class="plan-period">custom pricing</div>
      <ul class="plan-features">
        <li>Unlimited staff &amp; vehicles</li>
        <li>Dedicated workspace per organisation</li>
        <li>All Professional features</li>
        <li>Role-based access control</li>
        <li>Enterprise data migration</li>
        <li>Dedicated support</li>
        <li>Custom integrations</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/about" class="plan-cta secondary">Contact Us</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="faq">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Is there a free trial?</h3>
      <p>Contact us to arrange a trial workspace. We'll set up a fully functional environment so your team can evaluate Thermio before committing.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Can I manage multiple companies?</h3>
      <p>Yes. Each workspace operates independently with its own staff, assets, and settings.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>What happens to our data?</h3>
      <p>Data is stored securely with custom automatic log retention. You can export a full backup at any time.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<%- include('../partials/public-footer') %>
</body>
</html>
